Requirements:

	python 2.6 / python 2.7
	gcc
	g++

	
Installation:

	Copy the bin and share folders to /usr.


Running:

	To generate a template test case setup:

		c-extraction-test -g
		
	To run a set of test cases, run:

		c-extraction-test
		
	in the directory that contains the configuration file.

	If you need to run the script from another directory:

		c-extraction-test -d [DIRECTORY]
		
	For help:

		c-extraction-test -h
		

